notes.body: Hello Subba,     Greetings from PharmEasy!   ​   With regards to your order #658324296108748800-56675, I have checked the medicine TRIOHALE BOX OF 30 ROTACAPS has an expiry date of June 2026. I wish to inform you that we ensure that the shelf life of the medicines being supplied by our partner retailers is, at least, a minimum of 3 months from the date of delivery. As per the confirmation from our certified Pharmacist, If the expiry date of the medicine is beyond 3 months from the expiry, you can use that item. Thank you for choosing PharmEasy. Stay Healthy.     Regards,  Manisha
notes.body_html:
Hello Subba,

Greetings from PharmEasy! 
​
With regards to your order #658324296108748800-56675, I have checked the medicine TRIOHALE BOX OF 30 ROTACAPS has an expiry date of June 2026. I wish to inform you that we ensure that the shelf life of the medicines being supplied by our partner retailers is, at least, a minimum of 3 months from the date of delivery. As per the confirmation from our certified Pharmacist, If the expiry date of the medicine is beyond 3 months from the expiry, you can use that item.

If you still do not want this medicine then you can raise a return request for the item which is no longer required post the order delivery.
​
For any further assistance, please reach out to us through our support channels in the App or website listed in the 'Need Help' section.

Thank you for choosing PharmEasy. Stay Healthy.
